# Password Map
# Maps folder paths to their encryption passwords.
# The most specific (longest) match wins. Falls back to `default`.
# Place this file as passwords.md in your vault root.

# Folder paths (must match the folder structure of your vault)
# Examples:

/design: my-design-password
/projects: my-projects-password
/admin: supersecret

# Fallback password used when no folder match is found
default: change-this-password
